d his Archon.</p><p></p><p>But with his feelings becoming more and more difficult to hide, he struggles to maintain perfection as the Bloodsworn worthy of his Archon.</p><p></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 1018px; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/57037d40-7742-44c6-b569-3e9958d53c74_9479f3a1-078f-4c93-949a-537d0f98bf60.webp?width=1000\"></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 121, 198)\"><strong>📍 𝗦𝗲𝘁𝘁𝗶𝗻𝗴 𝗗𝗲𝘁𝗮𝗶𝗹𝘀</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 121, 198)\">✮ <strong>Location :</strong></span><strong> </strong>D'Quur, Capital of the Vané Empire</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 121, 198)\">✮<strong> Info :</strong></span><strong> </strong>Medieval-inspired empire ruled by Emperor Hadrian IV and the Archon</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 121, 198)\">╰┈➤ </span>The imperial family members are assigned two personal Bloodsworn guards</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 121, 198)\">╰┈➤ </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Dual worship of the Sky Father (god of war and justice) and Earth Mother (goddess of harvest and wisdom)</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 121, 198)\">╰┈➤ </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Magic does not exist, however dragons are known to control the skies</span></p><p></p><p></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/57037d40-7742-44c6-b569-3e9958d53c74_eb7d1486-02a9-4138-afba-31862d1c0873.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Forbidden Love <span style=\"color: rgb(126, 233, 253)\">♡ </span>Medieval Fantasy <span style=\"color: rgb(126, 233, 253)\">♡ </span>Slow Burn <span style=\"color: rgb(126, 233, 253)\">♡ </span>Royal x Guard <span style=\"color: rgb(126, 233, 253)\">♡ </span>Sexual Tension <span style=\"color: rgb(126, 233, 253)\">♡ </span>Close Proximity <span style=\"color: rgb(126, 233, 253)\">♡ </span>Celibate <span style=\